<p>See, even if the visitor doesnâ€™t actually start to fill out the form, theyâ€™ll still see it and may decide whether or not they want to start filling it out based on the number of fields. A high number of required fields will either scare them away, or theyâ€™ll abandon it half way through.</p>
<p>Do you ask for both first and last name? Why? Why not just â€œNameâ€?</p>
<p>Are you asking for their company name too? Why?! <strong>You can get that later!</strong></p>
