<p>Whatâ€™s the best practice? Itâ€™s widely accepted that orange is a great â€œclick colorâ€ because it creates the feeling of buying or selling, itâ€™s energetic. Both Unbounce and SiteTuners use it on their sites â€“ and theyâ€™re <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2019/07/25/ecommerce-user-experience">conversion rate optimization</a> companies, so they should know!</p>
