<h2>11. Stop Hoarding &amp; Remove Your Clutter</h2>
<p>You might think itâ€™s necessary to provide a visitor with all the benefits and everything you can offer on your landing page.</p>
<p><strong>Itâ€™s not.</strong></p>
<p>Sometimes removing unnecessary paragraphs can improve the experience for the visitor and make it easier to understand, thereby increasing conversion rates.</p>
<p>Remember, attention spans have never been lower than they are today.</p>
<p>So take a look at your site, and say goodbye to that prized paragraph youâ€™re so proud of.</p>
